data.description: Welcome to luxury living at its finest! Nestled in the highly sought-after Fairwood subdivision, this stunning 3-level, three bedrooms, three full bathrooms, one half bath, end-unit townhome with 3400+ sq. ft. exudes elegance and sophistication.  Backs to trees, providing desired privacy and steps from the walking trails and the lake.    Upon entering the home, you are greeted by a grand foyer adorned with ceramic tile, setting the tone for the lavish appointments throughout. The main level boasts a versatile rec room with sliding glass doors leading to a spacious backyard oasis, perfect for outdoor entertaining. A full bathroom and convenient access to the two-car garage complete the level, offering both functionality and style.  Ascend to the second level and be captivated by the open floor plan, accentuated by dramatic 9-foot ceilings. The formal living and dining rooms provide a graceful backdrop for hosting gatherings, while the updated kitchen with over-sized island, stainless steel appliances, double oven, gas cooktop and cabinetry galore will meet all your storage needs.  There is also a separate pantry.  Equipped with separate eat-in space that seamlessly flows into the cozy family room anchored by a fireplace—an ideal setting for relaxation and unwinding. This level has beautiful gleaming hardwood floors.  You will love the layout of this floor with all the windows and natural light! There is a half bath for convenience, that is neatly tucked away.  The family room will quickly become the oasis you crave.  With an abundance of windows overlooking the wooded backyard, it will be easy to just sit by the fireplace and decompress.   Retreat to the third level where luxury awaits in the expansive owner's suite featuring a sizable walk-in closet, offering a serene sanctuary to escape the hustle and bustle of everyday life. The Primary en-suite bath with separate jetted tub and shower, dual vanities, and private water closet. Two additional generously sized bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a convenient laundry room round out the upper level, providing ample space for family and guests.   Indulge in the array of amenities Fairwood has to offer, including a community center, swimming pools, tennis courts, playgrounds,  picturesque walking trails and ponds—perfect for enjoying the outdoors and fostering a sense of community.  Conveniently located with easy access to major routes such as 50 and I495, as well as the New Carrollton Metro station, commuting and exploring the surrounding area is a breeze. Additionally, a variety of shopping centers, grocery stores, and dining options are just moments away, ensuring effortless convenience at your fingertips.   Don't miss this rare opportunity to experience luxurious living in one of Fairwood's most coveted residences. Schedule your private tour today and prepare to embark on a lifestyle of unparalleled comfort and sophistication!  Hurry...Don't wait!!!!  Buyer's to receive 50% discount on title fees if they opt to use seller's preferred title.  OPEN HOUSE Sat. Feb 24 ---11am-2pm
